The,Openfit,API,is,an,open,source,software,framework,to,store,organize,and,analyze,fitness,data,collected,from,device,sensors,and,provide,access,to,all,data,and,functionality,through,open,APIs,The,open,fitness,platform,aims,to,meet,the,following,features,a,security,model,and,user,control,over,data,sharing,customizable,interface,infrastructure,to,develop,integration,with,new,vendor,devices,leverage,existing,open,source,solutions,and,operate,with,commercial,participants